results.description:
A big male elephant trying to reach the leaves and fruits of a tree in South Luangwa National Park, Zambia. Even  this huge animal was not tall enough to get to them, so he had to get up on its hind legs. What a sight! I guess that when you really want something you have to be willing to do something extra for it.
